報指，因保障疫情防控、城市運行、生產生活、特殊疾病治療等原因必須出城的人士，以及滯留在漢外地人士（以下簡稱出城人士）可以出城，但要堅持錯峯出城、分批實施，適時安全有序原則。出城人士不屬於被要求隔離的人員（包括確診患者、疑似患者、發熱患者、密切接觸者及處於觀察期的治癒出院患者），且須身體健康，沒有發燒、乾咳、氣喘等症狀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200224/PWKPATPYM5JMOWGR55EI2GQD3M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200224%2FPWKPATPYM5JMOWGR55EI2GQD3M%2F&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=1311d4c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200224%2FPWKPATPYM5JMOWGR55EI2GQD3M%2F&h=bab64e4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200224/PWKPATPYM5JMOWGR55EI2GQD3M/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>武漢獨立，唯一出路！<br />\n光復武漢，時代革命！</strong></span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:47:20.000Z","msg":"武漢人，報仇！"},{"pid":"b424ff452ee8a52c46dfac49cf6fdfa152c29ff8","tid":1894840,"uid":119810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e705acd67ce5e8778cdd51b6006ed4ccfdfdf93c","tid":1894840,"uid":155818,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"0796ff0af1c41d7612822ce155e17e15276d083b","tid":1894840,"uid":122275,"like":67,"dislike":3,"score":64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:31:56.000Z","msg":"美國真係做唔到咁啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:32:38.000Z","msg":"加州話唔定會做呢<br />\n佢地咁憎侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:47:32.000Z","msg":"加州大把華人 中得最多肺炎嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 獨立囉 咪累死美國"},{"pid":"3e9afa7fe761d95bf6baaf1dabf6778f9b00998c","tid":1894840,"uid":216103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce1dac9d589782a057b24dbd68177564cfe54e39","tid":1894840,"uid":120955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T07:55:47.000Z","msg":"解封嘅話其實省即刻封關獨立<img